Is this a voltage or a current reading?  ISENSE seems to indicate current but want to check and be sure.  If it is current, then the sensor name should be BB_ADC_FAN_ISENSE_CURR_A.

This is voltage of ISENSE pin of HSC. The current(BB_ADC_FAN_ISENSE_CURR_A) is calculated by virtual sensor with this voltage.
